org.jhove2.module.format.xml
Class SaxParser

java.lang.Object
  org.jhove2.core.reportable.AbstractReportable
      org.jhove2.module.format.xml.SaxParser
All Implemented Interfaces:
Reportable
@Persistent
public class SaxParser
extends AbstractReportable

This class provides an wrapper for methods used to create and initialize the SAX2 parser used to characterize an XML instance.

Author:
rnanders
See Also:
official website for SAX
, Sun's JAXP website
, Xerces2 Java Parser
